00:00:00.079 --> 00:00:04.710
My scholarships is a simple way to
search for Grand Valley scholarships it

00:00:04.710 --> 00:00:09.480
is an online scholarship application
system that integrates on GV

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:14.610
scholarships and is customized based on
your information the process is simple

00:00:14.610 --> 00:00:21.420
log on to GVSU edu forward slash my
scholarships and click on the sign in

00:00:21.420 --> 00:00:28.289
button login with your GV network ID and
password once you're logged in you're

00:00:28.289 --> 00:00:31.800
ready to start your general application
which includes your personal information

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:36.719
you enter in and your applicant record
this provides scholarship committee

00:00:36.719 --> 00:00:42.120
members with more information about you
here's a tip be sure to complete as much

00:00:42.120 --> 00:00:46.289
as you can in the general application
including extracurricular and community

00:00:46.289 --> 00:00:50.360
service involvement you never know what
committee members are looking for

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:56.100
resumes are also a great addition to any
application now that your general

00:00:56.100 --> 00:01:00.420
application is complete the fun begins
you can now review scholarship

00:01:00.420 --> 00:01:04.379
opportunities that are recommended for
you based on your qualifications

00:01:04.379 --> 00:01:09.510
remember recommended does not constitute
as qualified so be sure to read the

00:01:09.510 --> 00:01:13.470
scholarship description if you meet the
requirements you may need to answer

00:01:13.470 --> 00:01:18.689
additional questions such as answering
and attaching an essay all of the

00:01:18.689 --> 00:01:22.170
scholarships listed within the
application system vary based on

00:01:22.170 --> 00:01:26.640
interest academic performance in major
so it's best to look at the requirements

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:31.350
as well as deadlines the scholarship
cycle begins October 1st to search and

00:01:31.350 --> 00:01:35.340
apply for scholarships for the next
academic year and goes into a March 1st

00:01:35.340 --> 00:01:39.900
for most returning and transfer students
scholarships for new incoming freshmen

00:01:39.900 --> 00:01:45.360
the deadline is February 15th so be sure
to mark your calendars remember

00:01:45.360 --> 00:01:49.710
searching for scholarships doesn't have
to be a pain remember to start early and

00:01:49.710 --> 00:01:54.920
stay organized and if you have questions
we're always here to help

